%N A396440 Decimal expansion of Sum_{k>=1} (zeta(2*k)/k)*(1/10)^(2*k).
%D A396440 H. M. Srivastava and Junesang Choi, Zeta and q-Zeta Functions and Associated Series and Integrals, Elsevier Insights, 2011, p. 272, eq. (36).
%F A396440 Equals log((sqrt(5)+1)*Pi/10) = log(A094888/10) = log(phi*Pi/5), where phi is the golden ratio (A001622).
%F A396440 Equals log(Gamma(9/10)*Gamma(11/10)).
%e A396440 0.016503798474903247040426931551239495256877793032454...
%t A396440 RealDigits[Log[GoldenRatio*Pi/5], 10, 120, -1][[1]]
%o A396440 (PARI) log((sqrt(5)+1)*Pi/10)
